【Smart & Safe】It has dual-temperature sensors and accelerated sensors with STM32 chip. And it also has sleep mode and automatic over-heating warning.
【External power supply】DC5525 power port is compatible with DC 12-24V AC adapter/power bank/car power.It's convenient for both home repairing and filed repairing.
